Name Test/Libraries/List/dup
Synopsis Remove multiple occurrences of elements in a list. The first occurrence remains.
Function list[&T] dup(list[&T] lst)
Usage import List;
Examples 
rascal>import List;
ok
rascal>dup([3, 1, 5, 3, 1, 7, 1, 2]);
list[int]: [3,1,5,7,2]
